SCRIPT: SELECT DAT.period_ID, DAT.SCH , DAT.GL_CODE , DAT.GL_DES , DAT.TYP , DAT.SCHM_CODE, DAT.SCHM_DESC, DAT.ROI , DAT.CR_ROI , DAT.seg , DAT.CCY , CASE WHEN DAT.ANR_LCY <= 50000000 THEN 'A.<= 5 cr' ELSE 'B.> 5 cr' END AS GRANULARITY, COUNT(DAT.acct) AS acct , SUM(DAT.INT_ACC_MTD) AS INT_MTD , SUM(DAT.CR_ANR_LCY) AS CR_ANR_LCY , SUM(DAT.ANR_LCY) AS ANR_LCY , SUM(DAT.ENR_LCY) AS ENR_LCY FROM ( SELECT fbd.DATESKEY AS period_id , fbd.BRANCH_CODE AS SOL , da.ACCOUNT_ID AS acct , da.Customer_id , da.ACCOUNT_NAME , c.SHEDULE AS SCH , c.MAIN_HEAD_DESC , c.SUB_HEAD_1_DESC , c.SUB_HEAD_2_DESC , c.GPR_LEVL_DESC AS GL_DES , j.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION AS CUSTYP , n.code_description AS CUSTYPDESC , fbd.schm_type AS TYP , fbd.schm_code AS SCHM_CODE , da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE as acct_opn_date, fbd.c5code , fbd.npa_status , m.CODE_DESCRIPTION AS SCHM_DESC , fbd.CURRENCY_CODE AS CCY , fbd.CR_BAL_LCY AS ENR_LCY , fbd.DR_BAL_LCY , fbd.CR_AVG_BAL_LCY AS CR_ANR_LCY , fbd.AVG_BAL_LCY AS ANR_LCY , (fbd.NRML_ACCRUED_AMOUNT_CR_DLY_MTD * fbd.currency_rate) AS INT_ACC_MTD , fbd.currency_rate , fbd.SEGMENT_CODE AS seg , fdir.Interest_Rate AS ROI , fbd.Credit_Interest_Effective_Rate AS CR_ROI , fbd.Debit_Interest_Effective_Rate , fbd.CR_BAL_ORG , fbd.DR_BAL_ORG , fbd.START_DATE , fbd.MATURITY_DATE , fbd.contractual_maturity_days AS contr_mat , fbd.residual_maturity_days AS res_mat , (fbd.Sanct_lim * fbd.currency_rate) AS LIMIT_Amt , fbd.ENR_BAL_LCY , fbd.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE AS GL_CODE FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly fbd LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate fdir on fbd.ACID = fdir.ACID AND fdir.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND fdir.REPORT_DATE = (SELECT MAX(REPORT_DATE) from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate ) LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view da ON fbd.Account_No = da.Account_Number LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_glpl c ON fbd.GLPL_ID = c.GLPL_ID_New LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_date h ON fbd.Dateskey = h.Dateskey LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.customer.dim_customers_view j ON fbd.Customer_No = j.CUSTOMER_ID LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_branch k ON fbd.Branch_Code = k.Branch_Code and k.SOURCE_SYSTEM = ( select Branch_Source_System from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_branch_source_system where Branch_Source_System_Skey = 2 ) and k.etl_is_active = '1' LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code l ON fbd.NPA_Status = l.Code_Bkey AND l.Code_Type_ID = '92' LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code m ON fbd.Schm_code = m.Code_Bkey AND m.Code_Type_ID = '100' LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code n ON j.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION = n.Code_Bkey AND n.Code_Type_ID = '120' WHERE fbd.DATESKEY = ( select max(DATESKEY) as DATESKEY from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly) AND c.MAIN_HEAD_SR_NO = 3 AND FBD.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE BETWEEN '36000' AND '37999' ) DAT GROUP BY DAT.period_ID, DAT.SCH , DAT.GL_CODE , DAT.GL_DES , DAT.TYP , DAT.SCHM_CODE, DAT.SCHM_DESC, DAT.ROI , DAT.CR_ROI , DAT.seg , DAT.CCY , CASE WHEN DAT.ANR_LCY <= 50000000 THEN 'A.<= 5 cr' ELSE 'B.> 5 cr' END

COLUMN_ALIAS:
borrowermst.finacleubscustomerid, 
    borrowermst.borrowername, 
    borrowermst.accountno, 
    (SELECT segmentname FROM segmentmst WHERE segmentid=borrowermst.segmentid) AS segmentname, 
    (SELECT rmname FROM rmmst WHERE rmid=borrowermst.rmid) AS rmname, 
    (SELECT rmcode FROM rmmst WHERE rmid=borrowermst.rmid) AS rmcode, 
    dailyinterest.borrowerid, 
    NVL(lbhwr.baseinterestrate,0)+NVL(lbhwr.floatinterestrate,0) AS roi, 
    NVL(lbhwr.penalinterest,0) AS penalrate, 
    dailyinterest.interestos, 
    dailyinterest.penalinterestos, 
    dailyinterest.dailycalcdate AS dailycalcdate, 
    TO_CHAR(lbp.loanvaluedate, 'dd-mm-yyyy') AS startdate, 
    TO_CHAR(lbp.loanmaturitydate, 'dd-mm-yyyy') AS loanmaturitydate, 
    'INR' AS currency, 
    SUM(dailyinterest.principleos) AS principleos, 
    SUM(dailyinterest.CURRENTMONTHINTERESTACCRUED) AS CURRENTMONTHINTERESTACCRUED, 
    SUM(dailyinterest.CURNTMONTHPENALINTERESTACCRUED) AS CURNTMONTHPENALINTERESTACCRUED, 
    dailyinterest.ubsrefno, 
    lbhwr.srno, 
    (SELECT HubName FROM HubMst WHERE HubId=Lb.HubId) AS HubName, 
    (SELECT hubcode FROM HubMst WHERE HubId=Lb.HubId) AS hubcode, 
    (SELECT STATENAME FROM statemst WHERE STATEID=h.STATEID) AS STATENAME, 
    (SELECT ZONENAME FROM zonemst WHERE ZONEID=h.ZONEID) AS ZONENAME, 
    CASE 
        WHEN lbhwr.interestrepaymenttype=1 THEN 'Rear-End' 
        ELSE 'Monthly' 
    END AS InterestRepayment
SOURCE_TABLE_NAME: dailyinteresthistorymst dailyinterest,   WHRUSER.BorrowerMST borrowermst,   WHRUSER.lbwhrvaluationmst lbhwr,   WHRUSER.LBMst lb,   WHRUSER.lbloanprocessref lbp,   WHRUSER.HubMst h
SCRIPT:
WHERE h.HubId = Lb.HubId 
    AND dailyinterest.borrowerid = borrowermst.borrowerid 
    AND lbhwr.ubsrefno = dailyinterest.ubsrefno 
    AND lbhwr.whrinwardid = lbp.whrinwardid 
    AND lbp.LBId = lb.LBId 
    AND dailycalcdate = to_date(to_char(to_date(to_char(sysdate-1,'mm/dd/yyyy'),'mm/dd/yyyy HH24:MI:SS'), 'dd-mon-yyyy'),'dd-mon-yyyy') 
    GROUP BY borrowermst.finacleubscustomerid, 
    borrowermst.borrowername, 
    borrowermst.segmentid, 
    borrowermst.rmid, 
    dailyinterest.borrowerid, 
    dailycalcdate, 
    lbp.loanvaluedate, 
    lbp.loanmaturitydate, 
    dailyinterest.ubsrefno, 
    lbhwr.srno, 
    Lb.HubId, 
    dailyinterest.interestos, 
    dailyinterest.penalinterestos, 
    lbhwr.interestrepaymenttype, 
    lbhwr.baseinterestrate, 
    lbhwr.floatinterestrate,

			fbd.SEGMENT_CODE AS seg, 			fbd.CURRENCY_CODE AS CCY, 			CASE 				WHEN fbd.ACCOUNT_OPENEING_BALANCE * fbd.currency_rate <= 50000000 THEN '<= 5cr' ELSE 'B.> 5 cr' 			END AS GRANULARITY, 			da.ACCOUNT_ID AS acct, 			fbd.NRML_ACCRUED_AMOUNT_CR_DLY_MTD * fbd.currency_rate AS INT_ACC_MTD, 			fbd.CR_AVG_BAL_LCY AS ANR_LCY, 			fbd.CR_BAL_LCY AS ENR_LCY 		FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly fbd 		LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view da 			ON fbd.ACID = da.account_id /*da.ACCOUNT_NUMBER */ 		LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_glpl c 			ON fbd.GLPL_ID = c.GLPL_ID_New 		LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.customer.dim_customers_view j 			ON fbd.Customer_No = j.CUSTOMER_id 		LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code m 			ON fbd.Schm_code = m.Code_Bkey 			AND m.Code_Type_ID = '100' 		LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code n 			ON j.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION = n.Code_Bkey 			AND n.Code_Type_ID = '120' 		WHERE fbd.DATESKEY  = (select max(DATESKEY) as DATESKEY from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly)  /* Placeholder for Power BI parameter   */ 		AND c.MAIN_HEAD_SR_NO = 3 		AND fbd.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE BETWEEN '36000' AND '37999' 		AND fbd.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE NOT IN ('37010', '36030', '36830') 		AND fbd.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = '1' /*added on 17-02-2025 by VT */ 		AND m.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = '1' 		/* added on 17-02-2025 by VT 		 AND n.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = '1' 		 and c.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = '1'*/ 	) DAT GROUP BY DAT.period_ID, DAT.SCH, DAT.GL_CODE, DAT.GL_DES, DAT.TYP, DAT.seg, DAT.CCY, DAT.GRANULARITY

SCRIPT: SELECT DAT.transaction_post_date, DAT.GL_Sub_Head_Code, DAT.Part_Tran_Type, DAT.TRAN_CRNCY_CODE, DAT.CUSTYP_GRP, DAT.GRANULARITY, SUM(DAT.Tran_CRNCY_LCY) AS TRAN_INR FROM ( SELECT ft.transaction_post_date, ft.Customer_No, dc.CUSTOMER_NAME, ft.Account_No, ft.TRAN_CRNCY_CODE, ft.Tran_CRNCY_LCY, CASE 	WHEN DC.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION IN ('AG', 'CP', 'EA', 'EB', 'EC', 'ED', 'EG', 'EM', 'ES', 'EY', 'FA', 'FD', 'FE', 'FF', 'ID', 'RT', 'S1', 'S5', 'SA', 'SD', 'SP', 'RB') THEN 'A.NATURAL_PERSON' 	WHEN DC.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION IN ('AE', 'AT', 'AV', 'AZ', 'B1', 'B2', 'BA', 'BB', 'BD', 'BE', 'BF', 'BG', 'BH', 'BL', 'BO', 'BP', 'BR', 'BS', 'BV', 'BW', 'BX', 'BY', 'BZ', 'C1', 'C5', 'C8', 'CQ', 'D1', 'DA', 'DB', 'DD', 'DO', 'FI', 'HG', 'HH', 'HI', 'PF', 'PS', 'S2', 'S3', 'S4', 'S6') THEN '3.Institutional' 	ELSE '2.Corporate' END AS CUSTYP_GRP, CASE 	WHEN ft.Tran_CRNCY_LCY < 20000000 THEN 'A.less than 2 Cr' 	ELSE 'B.2 cr and more' END AS GRANULARITY, ft.GL_Sub_Head_Code, dc.SUBSECTOR_CODE, dc.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION AS Customer_Type, DimC1.Code_Description AS Customer_Description, ft.Part_Tran_Type FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.facttransactiondly ft LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.customer.dim_customers_view dc ON ft.CUSTOMER_NO = dc.Customer_id /*AND dc.isdelete = 0 */ LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code DimC1 ON DimC1.CODE_BKEY = dc.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION AND DimC1.Code_TYPE_NAME = 'CUST_TYPE_DESC' WHERE ft.dateskey = (select max(DATESKEY) as DATESKEY from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly) AND CAST(ft.GL_Sub_Head_Code AS INT) BETWEEN 33000 AND 37999 ) DAT GROUP BY DAT.transaction_post_date, DAT.GL_Sub_Head_Code, DAT.Part_Tran_Type, DAT.TRAN_CRNCY_CODE, DAT.CUSTYP_GRP, DAT.GRANULARITY

AS GRANULARITY, COUNT(DAT.acct) AS acct , SUM(DAT.ENR_LCY) AS ENR_LCY FROM ( SELECT fbd.DATESKEY AS period_id, fbd.BRANCH_CODE AS SOL , da.ACCOUNT_NUMBER AS acct , da.CUSTOMER_ID , /*CUSTOMER_ID */ da.ACCOUNT_NAME, /*ACCOUNT_NAME */ c.SHEDULE AS SCH , c.MAIN_HEAD_DESC , c.SUB_HEAD_1_DESC , c.SUB_HEAD_2_DESC , c.GPR_LEVL_DESC AS GL_DES , j.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION AS CUSTYP , n.code_description AS CUSTYPDESC , fbd.schm_code AS SCHM_CODE , da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE as acct_opn_date , fbd.c5code , fbd.npa_status , m.CODE_DESCRIPTION AS SCHM_DESC , fbd.CURRENCY_CODE AS CCY , fbd.CR_BAL_LCY AS ENR_LCY , fbd.DR_BAL_LCY , fbd.currency_rate , fbd.SEGMENT_CODE AS seg , fdir.Interest_Rate , fbd.Credit_Interest_Effective_Rate , fbd.Debit_Interest_Effective_Rate , fbd.CR_BAL_ORG , fbd.DR_BAL_ORG , fbd.START_DATE , fbd.MATURITY_DATE , fbd.Sanct_lim * fbd.currency_rate AS LIMIT_Amt, fbd.ENR_BAL_LCY , fbd.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE AS GL_CODE FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly fbd LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate fdir on fbd.ACID = fdir.ACID AND fdir.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND fdir.REPORT_DATE = ( SELECT MAX(REPORT_DATE) from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate ) LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view da ON fbd.ACID = da.ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_glpl c ON fbd.GLPL_ID = c.GLPL_ID_New AND c.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_date h ON fbd.Dateskey = h.Dateskey AND h.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.customer.dim_customers_view j ON fbd.Customer_No = j.CUSTOMER_ID LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_branch k ON fbd.Branch_Code = k.BRANCH_CODE and k.SOURCE_SYSTEM = ( select Branch_Source_System from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_branch_source_system where Branch_Source_System_Skey = 2 ) and k.etl_is_active = '1' LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code l ON fbd.NPA_Status = l.Code_Bkey AND l.Code_Type_ID = '92' AND l.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code m ON fbd.Schm_code = m.Code_Bkey AND m.Code_Type_ID = '100' AND m.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code n ON j.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION = n.Code_Bkey AND n.Code_Type_ID = '120' AND n.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 WHERE fbd.DATESKEY = ( select max(DATESKEY) as DATESKEY from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly) /* Previous day */ AND fbd.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND c.MAIN_HEAD_SR_NO = 3 AND fbd.CR_BAL_LCY > 0 ) AS DAT GROUP BY DAT.period_ID , DAT.SCH , DAT.GL_CODE , DAT.GL_DES , DAT.CUSTYP , DAT.CUSTYPDESC, DAT.seg , DAT.CCY , CASE WHEN Dat.ENR_LCY < 20000000 THEN 'A.less than 2 Cr' ELSE 'B.2 cr and more' END

COLUMN_ALIAS:
* FROM

(SELECT

     SUBSCRIBER_ACCT_NUM,

    SUBSCRIBER_NAME,

    PRAN_NO,

    NLCC_REG_NO,

    GENDER,

        LAST_DEBIT_DATE,

        SUB_NOMINEE_NAME,

        NOMINEE_DOB ,

        SUB_RELATION,

       row_number() over(partition BY SUBSCRIBER_ACCT_NUM order by LAST_DEBIT_DATE desc) as rn,

    PRAN_STATUS,

    DOB,

    UPLOADED_DATE,

    SUBSCRIBER_PENSION_AMT,

    SUBSCRIBER_CONTRIBUTION_AMT,

    PAYMENT_FREQUENCY,

    SUBSTR('',

    1,

    6) AS SOURCED_BY,

    ENTITY_SHORT_NAME AS BRANCH_ID

FROM

   (

    SELECT

       taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_NAME,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.NALO_REG_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.NLCC_REG_NO,

        taAddress.STATE,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_ACCT_NUM,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.PRAN_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_ADHAR_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.CUST_ID,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.DOB,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.GENDER,

                TANOMINEE.SUB_NOMINEE_NAME,

                TANOMINEE.NOMINEE_DOB,

                TANOMINEE.SUB_RELATION,

                TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG.LAST_DEBIT_DATE,

        taContact.MOBILE_NUM,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_CONTRIBUTION_AMT,

        SUM(taSubscriberRegLeg.AMT_TO_BE_DEDUCTED) AS Amount_paid,

        COUNT(*) AS paid_for_months,

        Tasubscriberregdtls.Subscriber_Pension_Amt,

        Tasubscriberregdtls.Pran_Status,

        Taentity.Entity_Desc,

        TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.CREATED_DATE,

        TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG.PAYMENT_FREQUENCY,

        TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.UPLOADED_DATE,

        TAENTITY.ENTITY_SHORT_NAME
SCRIPT:
taSubscriberRegDtls

    INNER JOIN IBL_ASBA.TA_SUBSCRIBER_REG_LEG TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG ON

        TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.PRAN_NO= TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG.PRAN_NO

    INNER JOIN IBL_ASBA.TA_ADDRESS TAADDRESS ON

        TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.SUBSCRIBER_ADDRESS = TAADDRESS.ADDRESS_ID

    INNER JOIN IBL_ASBA.TA_CONTACT TACONTACT ON

        TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.SUBSCRIBER_CONTACT = TACONTACT.CONTACT_ID

    INNER JOIN IBL_ASBA.TA_SUB_REG_NOMINEE_DTLS TANOMINEE on

       TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.SEQ_ID=TANOMINEE.SUB_SEQ_ID

    LEFT JOIN IBL_ASBA.Ta_Entity Taentity ON

        Taentity.Entity_Short_Name = Tasubscriberregdtls.Branch_Id

    WHERE

        taSubscriberRegLeg.DEBIT_FLG = '1'
 
    GROUP BY

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_NAME,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.NALO_REG_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.NLCC_REG_NO,

        taAddress.STATE,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_ACCT_NUM,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.PRAN_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_ADHAR_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.CUST_ID,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.DOB,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.GENDER,

                TANOMINEE.SUB_NOMINEE_NAME,

                TANOMINEE.NOMINEE_DOB,

                TANOMINEE.SUB_RELATION,

                 TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG.LAST_DEBIT_DATE,

        taContact.MOBILE_NUM,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_CONTRIBUTION_AMT,

        Tasubscriberregdtls.Subscriber_Pension_Amt,

        Tasubscriberregdtls.Pran_Status,

        taEntity.ENTITY_DESC ,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.CREATED_DATE,

        Tasubscriberregleg.Payment_Frequency,

        Tasubscriberregdtls.Uploaded_Date,

        taEntity.ENTITY_SHORT_NAME

UNION

    SELECT

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_NAME,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.NALO_REG_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.NLCC_REG_NO,

        taAddress.STATE,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_ACCT_NUM,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.PRAN_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_ADHAR_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.CUST_ID,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.DOB,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.GENDER,

                TANOMINEE.SUB_NOMINEE_NAME,

                TANOMINEE.NOMINEE_DOB,

                TANOMINEE.SUB_RELATION,
 
               TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG.LAST_DEBIT_DATE,

        taContact.MOBILE_NUM,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_CONTRIBUTION_AMT,

        0 AS Amount_paid,

        0 AS paid_for_months,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_PENSION_AMT,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.PRAN_STATUS,

        taEntity.ENTITY_DESC,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.CREATED_DATE,

        TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG.PAYMENT_FREQUENCY,

        TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.UPLOADED_DATE,

        TAENTITY.ENTITY_SHORT_NAME

    FROM

        IBL_ASBA.TA_SUBSCRIBER_REG_DTLS TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS

    INNER JOIN IBL_ASBA.TA_SUBSCRIBER_REG_LEG TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG ON

        TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.PRAN_NO = TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG.PRAN_NO

    INNER JOIN IBL_ASBA.TA_ADDRESS taAddress ON

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_ADDRESS = taAddress.ADDRESS_ID

    INNER JOIN IBL_ASBA.TA_CONTACT TACONTACT ON

        TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.SUBSCRIBER_CONTACT = TACONTACT.CONTACT_ID

    INNER JOIN IBL_ASBA.TA_SUB_REG_NOMINEE_DTLS TANOMINEE on

        TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.SEQ_ID=TANOMINEE.SUB_SEQ_ID

    LEFT JOIN IBL_ASBA.Ta_Entity Taentity ON

        Taentity.Entity_Short_Name = Tasubscriberregdtls.Branch_Id

    WHERE

        taSubscriberRegLeg.pran_no NOT IN(

            SELECT PRAN_NO

        FROM

            IBL_ASBA.TA_SUBSCRIBER_REG_LEG

        WHERE

            DEBIT_FLG = '1')

        AND taSubscriberRegLeg.DEBIT_FLG = '0'

          AND

         TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG.LAST_DEBIT_DATE <> null

    GROUP BY

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_NAME,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.NALO_REG_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.NLCC_REG_NO,

        taAddress.STATE,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_ACCT_NUM,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.PRAN_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_ADHAR_NO,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.CUST_ID,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.DOB,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.GENDER,

                 TANOMINEE.SUB_NOMINEE_NAME,

                 TANOMINEE.NOMINEE_DOB,

                TANOMINEE.SUB_RELATION,

                 TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG.LAST_DEBIT_DATE,

        taContact.MOBILE_NUM,

        taSubscriberRegDtls.SUBSCRIBER_CONTRIBUTION_AMT,

        Tasubscriberregdtls.Subscriber_Pension_Amt,

        Tasubscriberregdtls.Pran_Status,

        Taentity.Entity_Desc,

        Tasubscriberregdtls.Created_Date,

        TASUBSCRIBERREGLEG.PAYMENT_FREQUENCY,

        TASUBSCRIBERREGDTLS.UPLOADED_DATE,

        TAENTITY.ENTITY_SHORT_NAME)) WHERE rn=1 ORDER BY LAST_DEBIT_DATE desc

COLUMN_ALIAS: a.[report], a.[pis_ref_no], a.[acc_ref_no],a.[businessdate], a.[tradedate], a.crno, a.custname,a.accounttype, a.brokername, a.accno, a.contractno, a.lecno,a.[payin_amt], a.[payout_amt], a.[tds_amt], a.[apprvl_chgs], a.[amc_chgs], a.[trn_chgs], a.[trfin_chgs], a.[trfout_chgs], a.[bulk_chgs], a.[pms_chgs], a.[paymode], a.[vou_id] FROM ( SELECT 'DAILY' [report], a.systrnno [pis_ref_no], a.accrefno [acc_ref_no],CONVERT(VARCHAR(10), a.businessdate,103) [businessdate],CONVERT(VARCHAR(10), a.tradedate,103) [tradedate], b.crno, b.custname,b.accounttype, b.brokername, dbo.ember_decrypt (a.accno_encrypt, 'D',0,0) accno, c.contractno, c.lecno, CASE WHEN a.trncd = '07' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [payin_amt],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '05' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [payout_amt],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '06' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [tds_amt],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '01' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [apprvl_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '02' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [amc_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '03' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [trn_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '11' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [trfin_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '12' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [trfout_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '13' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [bulk_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '15' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [pms_chgs],d.gcdescription [paymode], e.sname [vou_id], a.customerno, a.customeracno

d.gcode = b.paymode AND d.gcgroup = 'PAYM' INNER JOIN PIS_NEW.dbo.generalcodes [e] ON e.gcode = a.trncd AND e.gcgroup = 'CHGS' WHERE a.businessdate BETWEEN @dFromDt AND @dToDt AND ((a.trncd = '05' AND (a.accno_encrypt, 'D',0,0) accno, c.contractno, c.lecno,CASE WHEN a.trncd = '07' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [payin_amt],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '05' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [payout_amt],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '06' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [tds_amt],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '01' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [apprvl_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '02' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [amc_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '03' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [trn_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '11' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [trfin_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '12' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [trfout_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '13' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [bulk_chgs],CASE WHEN a.trncd = '15' THEN a.trnamt ELSE 0 END [pms_chgs],d.gcdescription [paymode], e.sname [vou_id], a.customerno, a.customeracno FROM PIS_NEW.dbo.accountstransdaily [a] INNER JOIN PIS_NEW.dbo.vcustomerhelp [b] ON b.custclientno = a.custclientno INNER JOIN PIS_NEW.dbo.lectranhdr [c] ON c.lecno = a.sysrefno INNER JOIN PIS_NEW.dbo.generalcodes [d] ON d.gcode = b.paymode AND d.gcgroup = 'PAYM' INNER JOIN PIS_NEW.dbo.generalcodes [e] ON e.gcode = a.trncd AND e.gcgroup = 'CHGS' WHERE a.businessdate BETWEEN @dFromDt AND @dToDt AND ((a.trncd = '05' AND a.drcr = 'C') OR (a.trncd IN ('01', '02', '03', '06', '07', '11', '12', '13', '15') AND a.drcr = 'D')))a

WHEN A.Product_Cat = 'NHAI' THEN 'NHAI' WHEN A.Product_Cat = 'Digital' THEN 'Digital' WHEN A.Mapped_Channel IN ('EXCLUSIVE', 'Pioneer', 'International Business', 'RM EXCLUSIVE', 'VRM-NR Affluent', JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.relationship.dim_relationship_manager_channel AS C ON B.REL_MNGR_ECN = C.ECN and c.etl_is_active = 1 AND (C.RM_CHANNEL <> 'VRM' OR C.RM_CHANNEL IS NULL) LEFT JOIN '201004065174', '201004065556', '201004065471', '201004068786', '200998891189', '200998906029', '200998906036', '200999036749', '200999036824', '201003921105', '201004071472', '201004073834', '201004085967', '201004086001', '201004095867', '201004095294', '201004096796', '201004096789', '201004096772', '201004096802', '201013675151', '201021291769') AND (A.AC_Status = 'LIVE' OR A.AC_CLS_DT >= '2023-01-01') AND A.SEG_CODE <> 'IB' AND A.ACOPNDT <> CURRENT_DATE ) AS A GROUP BY A.Mapped_Channel, A.BRCODE, A.Insert_Date, A.CASA_Type, A.ETB_NTB_Flag, A.IPO_Flag, CASE WHEN A.Product_Cat = SELECT usr.id AS WMS_ID, usr.cif_id AS EQUATION_ID, usr.dedupe_id AS DEDUPE_ID, usr.name AS CUSTOMER_NAME, spa.account_number AS FOLIO_NUMBER, ins.name AS INSTRUMENT_NAME, ass.name AS TYPE_OF_INSTRUMENT, hol.total_invested_amount AS INVESTED_AMOUNT, hol.total_invested_amount AS MARKET_VALUE FROM {adb_curated_catalog}.valuefy.`wealthfy_transactional-holding` hol JOIN {adb_curated_catalog}.valuefy.`wealthfy_transactional-instrument` ins ON hol.fk_id_instrument = ins.id and ins.etl_is_active = 1 AND ins.is_active = 1 AND ins.fk_id_product = 6 JOIN {adb_curated_catalog}.valuefy.`wealthfy_transactional-asset` ass ON ins.fk_id_asset = ass.id and ass.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 JOIN {adb_curated_catalog}.valuefy.`wealthfy_transactional-service_provider_account` spa ON hol.fk_id_instrument = spa.id and spa.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 JOIN {adb_curated_catalog}.valuefy.`wealthfy_transactional-account` acc ON acc.id = spa.fk_id_account  and acc.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 JOIN {adb_curated_catalog}.valuefy.`wealthfy_transactional-user` usr ON usr.id = acc.fk_id_user_primary_holder and usr.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 WHERE hol.is_active = 1 and hol.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1;

WITH interest_rate as (SELECT ACID,INTEREST_RATE FROM  {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate where ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 and report_date = (select max(report_date) from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate)),AccountData AS ( SELECT da.Branch_Code AS br_code, CAST(current_date() - INTERVAL 1 DAY AS DATE) AS Insert_Date, fbd.Dateskey, da.ACCOUNT_NUMBER AS Account_no, da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE, CASE WHEN da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE >= '2023-04-01' AND da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE <= '2024-03-31' THEN 'FYI_2023_2024' WHEN da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE >= '2024-04-01' AND da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE <= '2025-03-31' THEN 'FYI_2024_2025' ELSE 'Existing' END AS ETB_NTB_Flag, DATE_FORMAT(da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE, 'MMM-yy') AS Acct_Open_Month_Year, DATE_FORMAT(da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE, 'yyyyMM') AS Acct_Open_Month_Year_key, da.CUSTOMER_ID AS Fcustno, da.ACCOUNT_NAME AS Customer_Name, da.SCHEME_TYPE AS schmtype, da.SCHEME_CODE AS prodtype, dc.Code_Description AS FD_Type, dcust.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION AS Custtype, dcd.Code_Description AS Custdesc, CAST(da.rcre_time AS DATE) AS entered_date, da.ACCOUNT_CLOSE_DATE AS Closure_date, da.Term_Value_Date AS Value_Date, da.TERM_MATURITY_DATE AS Maturity_date, IR.Interest_Rate AS Interest_Rate, fbd.Account_Openeing_Balance AS Original_Deal_amount, dcust.CUSTOMER_SUB_CLASSIFICATION_CODE AS segcode, CASE WHEN fbd.Avg_Bal_Lcy < 0 THEN 0 ELSE fbd.Avg_Bal_Lcy END AS ANR, CASE WHEN fbd.Enr_Bal_Lcy < 0 THEN 0 ELSE fbd.Enr_Bal_Lcy END AS ENR, C.RM_CHANNEL AS Mapped_Channel, CASE WHEN da.SCHEME_CODE IN ('PAYSC', 'PAYTD') THEN 'PAYTM' WHEN da.SCHEME_CODE IN ('TRMIC', 'RDMIC', 'RDMIB', 'RDMSI', 'RDMIS', 'TRMIS') THEN 'BFIL' WHEN da.SCHEME_CODE IN ('GRGEN', 'GRSNR') THEN 'GROWW' WHEN da.SCHEME_CODE IN ('TRGNA', 'TRSNA', 'TATXS', 'TATXN') THEN 'AirtelPB' WHEN (dcust.CUSTOMER_SUB_CLASSIFICATION_CODE = 'ML' OR da.FREE_CODE_4 = 'INDIE' OR TRIM(REPLACE(da.Seller_Bkey, 'IBL', '')) IN ('SIGZSRV21', 'SIGZYSRV21')) THEN 'Digital' WHEN C.RM_CHANNEL IN ('EXCLUSIVE', 'Pioneer', 'International Business', 'RM EXCLUSIVE', 'VRM-NR Affluent', 'Senior Premium Acquisition Manager - Affluent', 'Affluent Central', 'Affluent Synergy', 'Affluent_Unmapped', 'Affluent Business Owner', 'Pioneer Private', 'Affluent BO') THEN 'Affluent' WHEN da.Account_number IN ('100055560785', '100056025465', '100056400532', '100056711881', '100058255644', '100059786132', '100059847053', '100045148760', '100053437997', '100054284107', '155510021995') THEN 'NHAI' WHEN da.CUSTOMER_ID IN ('55213176', '58267847') THEN 'NHIDCL' WHEN da.CUSTOMER_ID IN ('62221508', '41256129', '35165956', '59499406', '57156330', '35165956', '41256129', '62221508', '59499406', '51801391', '51841380', '34598295') THEN 'PAYTMCIF' WHEN da.CUSTOMER_ID = '30712723' THEN 'IIFCL' WHEN C.RM_CHANNEL = 'FIPS' THEN 'FIPS' WHEN C.RM_CHANNEL = 'ECRM-LB' THEN 'ECRM-LB' WHEN C.RM_CHANNEL IN ('GBG', 'Central Government') THEN 'GBG' ELSE 'Branch Banking' END AS FD_Segment FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view da LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly_view fbd ON da.ACCOUNT_NUMBER = fbd.Account_no LEFT JOIN interest_rate IR on fbd.ACID = IR.acid LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.customer.dim_customers_view dcust ON da.CUSTOMER_ID = dcust.CUSTOMER_ID LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code dc ON da.SCHEME_CODE = dc.Code_Bkey AND dc.code_type_name = 'SCHEME_CODE' and dc.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code dcd ON dcust.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION = dcd.Code_Bkey AND dcd.code_type_name = 'CUST_TYPE_DESC' and dcd.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.relationship.dim_rm_srm_crm B ON da.CUSTOMER_ID = B.CUSTOMER_ID and B.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.relationship.dim_relationship_manager_channel C ON B.REL_MNGR_ECN = C.ECN and c.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 WHERE fbd.Dateskey = '20241030' AND da.SCHEME_TYPE = 'TDA' AND (dcust.CUSTOMER_SUB_CLASSIFICATION_CODE IN ('RT', 'RET', 'BR', 'BL', 'RA', 'IG', 'CCRT', 'CHC', 'LR', 'CAT1140123', 'ST', 'BE', 'AR', 'CFD', 'SST', 'SBR', 'GBS', 'GJB', 'PSGB', 'BCFD', 'ML', 'GJA', 'DIY', 'PAR') OR dcust.CUSTOMER_SUB_CLASSIFICATION_CODE IS NULL) AND da.SCHEME_CODE NOT IN ('TRMIC', 'RDMIC', 'RDMIB', 'RDMSI', 'RDMIS', 'TRMIS') AND dcust.CUSTOMER_SUB_CLASSIFICATION_CODE <> 'IB' AND (C.RM_CHANNEL <> 'VRM' OR C.RM_CHANNEL IS NULL)    ) SELECT A.br_code AS Branch_code, A.Insert_Date, A.Dateskey, A.FD_Segment AS Mapped_Segment, 'Term Deposit' AS Product_Type, 'OTH' AS IPO_Flag, COUNT(DISTINCT A.Fcustno) AS Count_Distinct_Customer, COUNT(A.Account_no) AS Count_Accounts, SUM(A.ENR) AS ENR FROM AccountData A GROUP BY A.br_code, A.Dateskey, A.FD_Segment, Insert_Date

ft.transaction_post_date AS tran_date , ft.value_date , da.term_value_date , da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE as acct_opn_date , da.term_maturity_date , fbd.CREDIT_INTEREST_EFFECTIVE_RATE , fdir.INTEREST_RATE , THEN 'C.10 to 50 crore' ELSE 'D.50 cr n more' END AS GRAN FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.facttransactiondly ft LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.customer.dim_customers_view dc ON ft.Customer_No = dc.CUSTOMER_ID and ft.etl_is_active = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view da ON ft.Account_no = da.ACCOUNT_NUMBER LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code DimC1 ON DimC1.CODE_BKEY = dc.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION and DimC1.etl_is_active = 1 AND DimC1.Code_TYPE_NAME = 'CUST_TYPE_DESC' LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly fbd ON ft.Account_no = fbd.Account_no AND fbd.dateskey = ( select max(DATESKEY) as DATESKEY from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly) LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate fdir on fbd.ACID = fdir.ACID AND fdir.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND fdir.REPORT_DATE = ( SELECT MAX(REPORT_DATE) from ft.GL_Sub_Head_Code AS INT) BETWEEN 33000 AND 37999 AND ft.Tran_CRNCY_LCY >= 20000000

'TMNRE' , 'TNNRE' , 'TPNRD' , 'TPNRE' , 'TRNRD' , 'TRNRE' , 'TRNRP' , 'TRNRS' , 'RDNEL' , 'RDNEM') THEN 'D.NRE' when fbd.schm_code in ('OD601', 'CANRO' , 'BNNRO' , 'NODAO' , 'NOOAO' , 'NOSCH' , 'RDNRM') then 'E.NRO' ELSE 'F.Other_Schme' END AS PRODUCT_GRP, CASE WHEN substring(FBD.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE, 1, 2) IN ('35') THEN '02.SBA' WHEN substring(FBD.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE, 1, 2) IN ('36', '37') THEN SCRIPT: WITH RM_CHANNEL_DETAIL_D AS ( SELECT * FROM ( SELECT *, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ecn ORDER BY RM_Channel DESC) AS row_nm FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.relationship.dim_relationship_manager_channel WHERE ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 ) t WHERE row_nm = 1 ), dsu_upi_D AS ( SELECT DISTINCT B.CUSTOMER_ID AS customer_no, date_format(A.TRANSACTION_DATE, 'MMMyy') AS TRANS_MONTH, 1 AS UPI_ACTIVE FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.digital_banking.fact_upi_transaction AS A LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view AS B ON A.ACCOUNT_NUMBER = B.ACCOUNT_NUMBER WHERE A.SYSTEM_code = 14 AND A.TRANSACTION_STATUS IN ('2220', '3035', '8004', '1016') AND A.ACCOUNT_NUMBER IS NOT NULL AND A.TRANSACTION_DATE BETWEEN date_add(trunc(current_date, 'month'), -1 * dayofmonth(current_date)) AND last_day(add_months(current_date, -1)) AND A.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 ), dsu_mb_nb_D_base AS ( SELECT B.CUSTOMER_ID AS customer_no, A.debit_account_number AS FIN_ACCOUNT_NO, SYSTEM_CODE, date_format(transaction_date, 'MMMyy') AS TRAN_MNT, MAX(CASE WHEN SYSTEM_CODE = 08 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NB_ACTIVE, MAX(CASE WHEN SYSTEM_CODE = 09 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS MB_ACTIVE FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.digital_banking.fact_mobile_banking_and_net_banking_individual_customer_transaction AS A LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view AS B ON A.debit_account_number = B.ACCOUNT_NUMBER WHERE financial_non_financial_flag = 1 AND upper(trim(transaction_status)) IN ('S', 'SUC') AND A.calendar_date_skey BETWEEN CAST(date_format(add_months(trunc(current_date, 'month'), -1), 'yyyyMMdd') AS INT) AND CAST(date_format(last_day(add_months(current_date, -1)), 'yyyyMMdd') AS INT) AND A.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 GROUP BY B.CUSTOMER_ID, debit_account_number, SYSTEM_CODE, date_format(transaction_date, 'MMMyy') ), dsu_mb_nb_D AS ( SELECT CUSTOMER_NO, TRAN_MNT, MAX(NB_ACTIVE) AS NB_ACTIVE, MAX(MB_ACTIVE) AS MB_ACTIVE FROM dsu_mb_nb_D_base GROUP BY CUSTOMER_NO, TRAN_MNT ), dsu_IC2_3_D_cust_lvl_base AS ( SELECT * FROM {adb_mart_catalog}.enterprise_mart.fact_product_holding WHERE report_date = (SELECT MAX(report_date) FROM {adb_mart_catalog}.enterprise_mart.fact_product_holding) AND SA_FLAG = 1 ), dsu_IC2_3_D_cust_lvl AS ( SELECT A.BRCODE, A.report_date, current_date() - 1 AS Insert_Date, coalesce(I.RM_Channel, J.DESIGNATION_CODE) AS debug_channel_source, CASE WHEN upper(trim(coalesce(I.RM_Channel, J.DESIGNATION_CODE))) IN ( 'EXCLUSIVE','PIONEER','INTERNATIONAL BUSINESS','RM EXCLUSIVE', 'VRM-NR AFFLUENT','SENIOR PREMIUM ACQUISITION MANAGER - AFFLUENT', 'AFFLUENT CENTRAL','AFFLUENT SYNERGY','AFFLUENT_UNMAPPED', 'AFFLUENT BUSINESS OWNER','PIONEER PRIVATE','AFFLUENT BO' ) THEN 'AFFLUENT' WHEN upper(trim(coalesce(I.RM_Channel, J.DESIGNATION_CODE))) LIKE '%PIONEER%' THEN 'AFFLUENT' WHEN upper(trim(coalesce(I.RM_Channel, J.DESIGNATION_CODE))) LIKE '%EXCLUSIVE%' THEN 'AFFLUENT' WHEN upper(trim(coalesce(I.RM_Channel, J.DESIGNATION_CODE))) LIKE '%AFFLUENT%' THEN 'AFFLUENT' WHEN upper(trim(coalesce(I.RM_Channel, J.DESIGNATION_CODE))) = 'FIPS' THEN 'FIPS' WHEN upper(trim(coalesce(I.RM_Channel, J.DESIGNATION_CODE))) = 'ECRM-LB' THEN 'ECRM-LB' WHEN upper(trim(coalesce(I.RM_Channel, J.DESIGNATION_CODE))) IN ('GBG', 'CENTRAL GOVERNMENT') THEN 'GBG' WHEN upper(trim(coalesce(I.RM_Channel, J.DESIGNATION_CODE))) LIKE 'BPD%' THEN 'UNMAPPED' ELSE 'BRANCH BANKING' END AS MAPPED_CHANNEL, (SA_FLAG + CA_FLAG + FD_FLAG + CREDIT_CARD_FLAG + LI_FLAG + MF_FLAG + BROK_FLAG + LOCK_FLAG + HEALTH_FLAG + ACCI_FLAG + DP_FLAG + FX_FLAG + TR_FLAG + FCNR_FLAG + BBG_FLAG + PREMIUM_DC + CASE WHEN BL_FLAG = 1 OR GL_FLAG = 1 OR LACR_FLAG = 1 OR LAP_FLAG = 1 OR LAS_FLAG = 1 OR PL_FLAG = 1 OR HL_FLAG = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN FX_FLOW_FLAG = 1 OR FX_FORWARD_FLAG = 1 OR FX_OTHERS_FLAG = 1 OR FX_FCNR_FLAG = 1 OR FX_TRAVEL = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS REV_PH, IFNULL(B.UPI_ACTIVE, 0) AS PREV_MONTH_UPI_ACTIVE, IFNULL(E.NB_ACTIVE, 0) AS PREV_MONTH_NB_ACTIVE, IFNULL(E.MB_ACTIVE, 0) AS PREV_MONTH_MB_ACTIVE, CREDIT_CARD_FLAG AS CC_Penetration FROM dsu_IC2_3_D_cust_lvl_base A LEFT JOIN dsu_upi_D B ON A.cust_id = B.customer_no AND upper(B.TRANS_MONTH) = upper(date_format(add_months(current_date(), -1), 'MMMyy')) LEFT JOIN dsu_mb_nb_D E ON A.cust_id = E.customer_no AND upper(E.TRAN_MNT) = upper(date_format(add_months(current_date(), -1), 'MMMyy')) LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.relationship.dim_rm_srm_crm H ON A.cust_id = H.CUSTOMER_ID AND H.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN RM_CHANNEL_DETAIL_D I ON H.REL_MNGR_ECN = I.ECN LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.hrms.dim_employee J ON H.REL_MNGR_ECN = J.EMPLOYEE_ID AND J.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 ), dsu_IC2_3_D_summ as ( select brcode, report_date, mapped_channel, cast(avg(REV_PH*100*.01) AS DECIMAL(38,6)) as Revenue_PH, cast(sum(PREV_MONTH_UPI_ACTIVE) as INT) as M1_UPI_ACTIVE, cast(sum(PREV_MONTH_NB_ACTIVE) as INT) as M1_NB_ACTIVE,cast(sum(PREV_MONTH_MB_ACTIVE) as INT) as M1_MB_ACTIVE, cast(sum(CC_Penetration) as INT) as CC_Penetration, Insert_Date from dsu_IC2_3_D_cust_lvl group by brcode, report_date, mapped_channel, Insert_Date	 ) SELECT * FROM dsu_IC2_3_D_summ

SCRIPT: WITH temp5 AS ( SELECT DISTINCT DATE_FORMAT(current_date() - INTERVAL 1 DAY, 'yyyyMMdd') AS Dateskey, A.BRCODE AS Branch_code, current_date() - INTERVAL 1 DAY AS Insert_Date, CASE WHEN A.SCHMTYPE IN ('ODA', 'CAA', '') THEN 'CA' ELSE 'SA' END AS Product_Type, 'Live' AS Active_Inactive_Flag, A.CUSTID AS Customer_ID FROM {adb_mart_catalog}.enterprise_mart.ac_data_final A LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.relationship.dim_rm_srm_crm B ON A.CUSTID = B.CUSTOMER_ID and b.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.relationship.dim_relationship_manager_channel C ON B.REL_MNGR_ECN = C.ECN and C.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_mart_catalog}.enterprise_mart.md_ipo_list D ON A.Account = D.Account WHERE A.PRODTYPE NOT IN ('CNHAI', 'CNHID') AND A.Account NOT IN ( '201001686563', '201002547993', '201002778618', '201002979640', '201003173856', '201003195926', '201003196008', '201003196473', '201003445274', '201003441931', '201003438108', '201004019818', '201004062975', '201004062623', '201004062951', '201004062807', '625000000968', '201004065174', '201004065556', '201004065471', '201004068786', '200998891189', '200998906029', '200998906036', '200999036749', '200999036824', '201003921105', '201004071472', '201004073834', '201004085967', '201004086001', '201004095867', '201004095294', '201004096796', '201004096789', '201004096772', '201004096802', '201013675151', '201021291769' ) AND A.AC_Status = 'LIVE' AND A.ACTIVE_INACTIVE IN ('A', 'I', 'D') AND A.SEG_CODE <> 'IB' AND A.ACOPNDT <> current_date() AND ( C.RM_CHANNEL <> 'VRM' OR C.RM_CHANNEL IS NULL ) AND ( D.Month_IPO IS NULL OR D.Month_IPO = 'OTH' ) ), temp4 AS ( SELECT a.Customer_ID AS custid, a.Branch_code AS brcode, a.Insert_Date, a.Product_Type AS casa_type, b.DATE_OF_BIRTH, b.SOURCE_OF_INCOME, FLOOR(DATEDIFF(current_date() - INTERVAL 1 DAY, b.DATE_OF_BIRTH) / 365) AS age, TRY_CAST(TRIM(REPLACE(b.SOURCE_OF_INCOME, ',', '')) AS BIGINT) * 1 AS income FROM temp5 a LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.customer.dim_customers_view b ON a.Customer_ID = b.CUSTOMER_ID ), temp5_final AS ( SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN age < 15 THEN '0-14' WHEN age < 25 THEN '15-24' WHEN age < 35 THEN '25-34' WHEN age < 45 THEN '35-44' WHEN age < 60 THEN '45-59' ELSE '60+' END AS age_bracket, CASE WHEN income = 0 THEN '0' WHEN income NOT IN (11, 12, 13, 14, 15, 16, 17) AND income > 0 AND income < 75000 THEN '11' WHEN income / 12 >= 75000 AND income / 12 < 150000 THEN '12' WHEN income / 12 >= 150000 AND income / 12 < 300000 THEN '13' WHEN income / 12 >= 300000 AND income / 12 < 500000 THEN '14' WHEN income / 12 >= 500000 AND income / 12 < 1000000 THEN '15' WHEN income / 12 >= 1000000 AND income / 12 < 5000000 THEN '16' WHEN income / 12 >= 5000000 THEN '17' END AS income_bracket FROM temp4 A ) SELECT brcode, casa_type, income_bracket, age_bracket, COUNT(*) AS cnt, current_date() - INTERVAL 5 DAY AS Insert_Date FROM temp5_final GROUP BY brcode, casa_type, income_bracket, age_bracket, Insert_Date;

SELECT trim(A.ACCOUNT_NUMBER) AS LAN_No, CAST( trim(COALESCE(B1.flow_amt, B.FLOW_AMOUNT)) AS INT ) AS Disbursed_Amt, CAST(trim(C.CHRGE_AMT_COLLECTED / 1.18) as int) AS Net_PF_Amount, DATE_FORMAT( last_day(add_months(current_date(), -1)), 'MMM-yy' ) AS Month FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT ACCOUNT_ID, ACCOUNT_NUMBER, ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE, ACCOUNT_NAME FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view WHERE SCHEME_CODE IN ( 'LA796', 'LA795', 'LA794', 'LA793', 'LA792', 'LA791', 'LA744', 'LA740', 'LA736', 'LA734', 'LA730', 'LA728', 'LA727', 'LA723', 'LA722', 'LA716', 'LA715', 'LA714', 'LA713', 'LA712', 'LA711', 'LA703', 'LA702', 'LA701' ) AND ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE BETWEEN date_trunc('month', add_months(current_date(), -1)) AND last_day(add_months(current_date(), -1)) ) A LEFT JOIN ( SELECT DISTINCT ADVANCE_ACCOUNT_ID, FLOW_AMOUNT FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.loans.fact_loan_disbursement WHERE FLOW_ID IN ('DISBM') and etl_is_active = 1 ) B ON B.ADVANCE_ACCOUNT_ID = A.ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT DISTINCT ACID, FLOW_AMT FROM {adb_curated_catalog}.finacle.`tbaadm-ltdh` WHERE FLOW_ID IN ('DISBM') and etl_is_active = 1 ) B1 ON B1.acid = A.ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT acid, SUM(CHRGE_AMT_COLLECTED) AS CHRGE_AMT_COLLECTED FROM {adb_curated_catalog}.finacle.`tbaadm-chat` WHERE UPPER(PTTM_EVENT_ID) IN ( 'PERSONAL LOAN PROSF FEES', 'PL PROCESSING FEES D' ) and etl_is_active = 1 GROUP BY acid ) C ON C.acid = A.ACCOUNT_ID;

CUSTOMER_ID AND B.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.relationship.dim_relationship_manager_channel C ON B.     REL_MNGR_ECN = C.ECN AND C.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND ( C.RM_CHANNEL <> 'VRM' OR C.RM_CHANNEL IS NULL ) WHERE da.SCHEME_TYPE = 'TDA' AND da.SCHEME_CODE NOT IN ('TRMIC', 'RDMIC', 'RDMIB', 'RDMSI', 'RDMIS', 'TRMIS') ) SELECT br_code AS Branch_code, Insert_Date, Dateskey, FD_Segment AS Mapped_Segment, Mapped_Channel, ETB_NTB_Flag, 'Term Deposit' AS Product_Type, 'OTH' AS IPO_Flag, COUNT(ACCOUNT_NUMBER) AS Count_Accounts, SUM(ENR) AS ENR FROM BaseData GROUP BY br_code, Dateskey, FD_Segment, Mapped_Channel, ETB_NTB_Flag, Insert_Date

CASE WHEN RM.RM_CHANNEL IN ('EXCLUSIVE' , 'PIONEER' , 'Affluent_Unmapped', 'International Business') THEN 'A.AFFLUENT' ELSE 'B.Others' END as RM_CHANNEL, CASE WHEN fbd.SEGMENT_CODE IN ('AR' , 'BE' , 'IIG', 'LP' , 'AL' , 'MG' , 'SC' , 'CF') THEN '02.CII' ELSE '01.FIPS' END as BU, CASE WHEN fbd.schm_code IN ('ORFCN', 'TDFCN' , 'TMFCN' , 'TNFCN' , 'TRFBS' , 'TRFCN' , 'TRFQS') THEN 'A.FCNR' WHEN fbd.schm_code IN ('CALBO', 'SBLBO') THEN 'B.LBO' WHEN fbd.schm_code IN ('SBBCA', 'SBMIC') THEN 'C.MFI' WHEN fbd.schm_code IN ('CANRE', 'NEOAO' , 'NESCH' , 'NRDAO' , 'SBNAO' , 'SBNJO' , 'SBNRE' , 'SBNRH' , 'SBNRL' , 'SBNRS' , 'SBNSE' , 'SBNEP' , 'SBNIP' , 'SBNES' , 'SBNEE' , 'SBNEM' , 'SBNSE' , 'CNNRE' , 'CRNRE' , 'OMNNE' , 'OMRNE' , 'ONNRE' , 'ORNRE' , 'TDSNE' , 'TMNHP' , 'TMNRE' , 'TNNRE' , 'TPNRD' , 'TPNRE' , 'TRNRD' , 'TRNRE' , 'TRNRP' , 'TRNRS' , 'RDNEL' , 'RDNEM') THEN 'D.NRE' WHEN fbd.schm_code IN ('OD601', 'CANRO' , 'BNNRO' , 'NODAO' , 'NOOAO' , 'NOSCH' , 'NROFS' , 'NROLR' , 'SBNEW' , 'SBNOH' , 'SBNRB' , 'SBNRO' , 'SBNOP' , 'SBNRP' , 'SBNFT' , 'SBNOS' , 'SBNOE' , 'SBNOM' , 'SBNSO' , 'CNNRO' , 'CRNRO' , 'OMNRO' , 'ONNRO' , 'ORNRO' , 'TDSNO' , 'TDSNS' , 'TMNOD' , 'TMNOH' , 'TMNR' , 'TMNRO' , 'TMNTS' , 'TNNOD' , 'TNNOH' , 'TNNRO' , 'TNNTS' , 'TNRBO' , 'TPNRO' , 'TRNOD' , 'TRNOP' , 'TRNOS' , 'TRNRO' , 'TRNSS' , 'TRNTS' , 'TRRBO' , 'TRSSS' , 'RDNRL' , 'RDNRM') THEN 'E.NRO' ELSE 'F.Other_Schme' END as PRODUCT_GRP, CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(FBD.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE,1,2) IN ('35') THEN '02.SBA' WHEN SUBSTRING(FBD.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE,1,2) IN ('36', '37') THEN '03.TDA' ELSE '01.CAA' END as GL_GRP , J.Customer_Type_Description as CUSTYP , N.code_description as CUSTYPDESC, fbd.schm_code as SCHM_CODE , CASE WHEN da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE <= '2020-02-01' THEN '01.more than 1 Yr' WHEN cr n more' END as GRAN , da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE , fbd.c5code , fbd.npa_status , M.CODE_DESCRIPTION AS SCHM_DESC , fbd.CURRENCY_CODE as CCY , fbd.CR_BAL_LCY as ENR_LCY , fbd.CR_AVG_BAL_LCY as ANR_LCY , AND fdir.REPORT_DATE = (SELECT MAX(REPORT_DATE) from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate ) LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view da ON fbd.ACID = da.Account_ID AND da.SOURCE_SYSTEM IN ('SAVING_ACC' , 'CURRENT_ACC' , 'TERM_DEPOSIT_ACC', 'LOAN_ACC' , 'OFFICE_ACC') LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_glpl C ON fbd.GLPL_ID {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.customer.dim_customers_view J ON fbd.Customer_no = J.Customer_ID AND J.SOURCE_SYSTEM IN ('IND', 'ORG') LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_branch K ON K.ETL_IS_ACTIVE =1 LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code L ON fbd.NPA_Status =L.Code_Bkey and Code_Type_ID ='92' AND L.ETL_IS_ACTIVE=1 LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code M on fbd.Schm_code =M.Code_Bkey and M.Code_Type_ID ='100' AND M.ETL_IS_ACTIVE=1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code N ON J.Customer_Type_Description = N.Code_Bkey AND N.ETL_IS_ACTIVE =1 AND N.Code_Type_ID = '120' AND N.ETL_IS_ACTIVE =1 LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code O on O.CODE_BKEY = fbd.c5code and o.Code_Type_ID ='109' AND O.ETL_IS_ACTIVE=1 AND O.ETL_IS_ACTIVE=1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.relationship.dim_rm_srm_crm CRM ON CRM.CUSTOMER_ID = J.CUSTOMER_ID AND CRM.ETL_IS_ACTIVE=1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.relationship.dim_relationship_manager_channel RM ON RM.ECN = CRM.REL_MNGR_ECN AND RM.ETL_IS_ACTIVE=1 WHERE fbd.DATESKEY = SCRIPT: with Date_cte AS ( SELECT DATE_FORMAT(DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', ADD_MONTHS(CURRENT_DATE(), -1 )), 'yyyy-MM-dd') AS prev_month_start_date, DATE_FORMAT(LAST_DAY(ADD_MONTHS(CURRENT_DATE(), -1)),'yyyy-MM-dd') AS prev_month_end_date ) ,  FX_RATES AS ( SELECT YEAR(CAST(VALUE_DATE AS DATE)) AS Year, MONTH(CAST(VALUE_DATE AS DATE)) AS Month, DAY(CAST(VALUE_DATE AS DATE)) AS Month_Date, CAST(VALUE_DATE AS DATE) AS ETL_CREATED_DATE, DATE_SUB(CAST(VALUE_DATE AS DATE), 1) AS Curr_Value_Date, CURRENCY_CODE, FOREIGN_EXCHANGE_RATE_TO_BASE FROM ( SELECT YEAR(CAST(VALUE_DATE AS DATE)) AS Year, MONTH(CAST(VALUE_DATE AS DATE)) AS Month, DAY(CAST(VALUE_DATE AS DATE)) AS Month_Date, CAST(VALUE_DATE AS DATE), DATEADD(DAY, -1, CAST(VALUE_DATE AS DATE)) AS Actual_Value_Date, CURRENCY_CODE, FOREIGN_EXCHANGE_RATE_TO_BASE FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog} .forex.fact_forex_conversion WHERE CURRENCY_CODE IS NOT NULL ) AS sub_fx ), TRANSACTIONS_ENRICHED AS ( SELECT A.BEV_FINISHED_DATE, YEAR(A.BEV_FINISHED_DATE) AS Tran_Year, MONTH(A.BEV_FINISHED_DATE) AS Tran_Month, DAY(A.BEV_FINISHED_DATE) AS Month_Day, A.DATES_KEY, A.BRANCH_CODE_INPUT, A.BRANCH_CODE_BEHALF, A.BRANCH_NAME, A.PRODUCT, A.PRODUCT_NAME, A.SUB_PRODUCT_NAME, A.MAS_MASTER_REFERENCE, A.BILL_REFERENCE, A.EVENT_NAME, A.TRANSACTION_DATE, A.CUSTOMER_NUMBER, A.CUSTOMER_NAME, B.CUSTOMER_SUB_CLASSIFICATION_CODE, A.PURPOSE_CODE, A.EVENT_AMOUNT, COALESCE(A.TRANSACTION_AMOUNT, 0) AS TRANSACTION_AMOUNT, A.TRANSACTION_CURRENCY, A.ACCOUNT_NUMBER, A.SEGMENT_CODE, COALESCE( C.FOREIGN_EXCHANGE_RATE_TO_BASE, COALESCE(prev.FOREIGN_EXCHANGE_RATE_TO_BASE, 0) ) AS Rate FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog} .trade_finance.fact_trade_transaction_mis A LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog} .customer.dim_customers_view B ON A.CUSTOMER_NUMBER = B.CUSTOMER_ID LEFT JOIN FX_RATES C ON A.TRANSACTION_CURRENCY = C.CURRENCY_CODE AND CAST(A.BEV_FINISHED_DATE AS DATE) = C.CURR_VALUE_DATE LEFT JOIN ( SELECT CURRENCY_CODE, CURR_VALUE_DATE, FOREIGN_EXCHANGE_RATE_TO_BASE FROM ( SELECT *, ROW_NUMBER() OVER ( PARTITION BY CURRENCY_CODE, CURR_VALUE_DATE ORDER BY CURR_VALUE_DATE DESC ) AS rn FROM FX_RATES ) prev_fx WHERE rn = 1 ) prev ON A.TRANSACTION_CURRENCY = prev.CURRENCY_CODE AND prev.CURR_VALUE_DATE < CAST(A.BEV_FINISHED_DATE AS DATE) left join Date_cte dateCTE on 1=1 WHERE CAST(A.BEV_FINISHED_DATE AS DATE) BETWEEN dateCTE.prev_month_start_date AND dateCTE.prev_month_end_date AND ( A.EVENT_NAME LIKE 'Create%' OR A.EVENT_NAME LIKE 'Issue%' OR A.EVENT_NAME LIKE 'Amend%' OR A.EVENT_NAME LIKE 'Advise%' ) AND A.CUSTOMER_NUMBER NOT LIKE '%IRV%' AND A.CUSTOMER_NUMBER NOT LIKE '%CP%' AND A.CUSTOMER_NUMBER NOT LIKE '%CITI%' AND A.CUSTOMER_NUMBER NOT LIKE '%DABA%' AND A.CUSTOMER_NUMBER NOT LIKE '%BELAD%' ), CTE_TRANSACTIONS AS ( SELECT te.*, te.TRANSACTION_AMOUNT * te.Rate AS Tran_Value_LCY FROM TRANSACTIONS_ENRICHED te ), dimcustomer AS ( SELECT DISTINCT customer_id, customer_name FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog} .customer.dim_individual_customer WHERE etl_is_active = '1' UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT customer_id, customer_name FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog} .customer.dim_organization_customer WHERE etl_is_active = '1' ), asset_mntly_inc AS ( SELECT DISTINCT customer_no, rm, rm_code, zone, Zonal_Head_Name, Zonal_Head_ECN FROM {adb_mart_catalog}.enterprise_mart.it_asset_mntly_inc UNION SELECT DISTINCT customer_no, rm, rm_code, zone, Zonal_Head_Name, Zonal_Head_ECN FROM {adb_mart_catalog}.enterprise_mart.liability_mntly_inc ), segemnt_mapper_ccbg AS ( SELECT SUB_SEGMENT, BUSINESS_UNIT_2_DESCRIPTION FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog} .mapping.dim_segment_mapper_ccbg WHERE ETL_IS_ACTIVE = '1' ) SELECT date_format(last_day(date_add(current_date(), -31)), 'yyyyMMdd') AS Period_id, date_format(last_day(date_add(current_date(), -31)), 'yyyy/MM/dd') AS New_Period_ID, base.ACCOUNT_NUMBER AS Account_no, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  Acct_Opn_Date, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  Acct_Cls_Date, base.CUSTOMER_NUMBER AS Customer_No, base.customer_name AS Customer_Name, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  SCHM_CODE, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  Schm_type, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  ANR, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  ENR, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  ANR_ZERO, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  ENR_ZERO, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  Customer_Open_Date, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  End_date, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  INDUSTRY_CODE, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  NPA_Status, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  NPA_IND, a.rm_code, a.rm, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS USER_Region, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS GROUP_ID, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS CURRENCY, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS CURRENCY_RATE, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS Sanction_limit, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS Sanction_limit_calc, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS Utilization_Ratio, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS RM_Branch_Code, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS Branch_Code, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS External_Rating, base.CUSTOMER_SUB_CLASSIFICATION_CODE AS SEGMENT_CODE, b.BUSINESS_UNIT_2_DESCRIPTION AS BU, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  FB_NFB, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  TL_WC, a.zone, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS  Account_Status, 'TF' AS PRODUCT, base.PRODUCT_NAME AS SUB_PRODUCT_1, base.SUB_PRODUCT_NAME AS SUB_PRODUCT_2, base.EVENT_NAME AS SUB_PRODUCT_3, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS CALLABLE_NONCALLABLE_FLAG, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS ACTIVE_ASSET, CASE WHEN a.rm_code IS NOT NULL AND a.rm_code <> '' THEN a.rm_code WHEN ( a.rm_code = 'IBL' OR a.rm_code = '' ) THEN a.Zonal_Head_ECN WHEN ( a.Zonal_Head_ECN IS NULL OR a.Zonal_Head_ECN = '' OR a.Zonal_Head_ECN = 'Unmapped' ) THEN 'Unmapped' ELSE 'Unmapped' END AS RM_CODE_NEW, a.Zonal_Head_ECN, a.Zonal_Head_Name, ( CASE WHEN a.rm_code IS NOT NULL AND a.rm_code <> '' THEN a.rm_code WHEN ( a.rm_code = 'IBL' OR a.rm_code = '' ) THEN a.Zonal_Head_ECN ELSE 'Unmapped' END || '-' || b.BUSINESS_UNIT_2_DESCRIPTION || '-' || a.Zonal_Head_Name ) AS RM_Seg_ZH_Key, CASE WHEN base.TRANSACTION_CURRENCY = 'USD' THEN SUM( CASE WHEN base.TRANSACTION_CURRENCY = 'USD' THEN COALESCE(base.Tran_Value_LCY, 0) END ) / NULLIF( AVG( CASE WHEN base.TRANSACTION_CURRENCY = 'USD' THEN RATE END ), 0 ) END AS TF_THROUGHPUT_USD, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS CMS_THROUGHPUT_LACS, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS TAX_LACS, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS SALARY_CREDIT_LACS, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS Free_text_1, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS Free_text_2, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS Free_text_3, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS Free_text_4, CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS Free_text_5 FROM CTE_TRANSACTIONS base inner join dimcustomer cust ON base.CUSTOMER_NUMBER = cust.customer_id LEFT JOIN asset_mntly_inc a ON base.CUSTOMER_NUMBER = a.customer_no LEFT JOIN segemnt_mapper_ccbg b ON base.SEGMENT_CODE = b.SUB_SEGMENT GROUP BY base.CUSTOMER_NUMBER, base.CUSTOMER_NAME, cust.customer_name, base.PRODUCT_NAME, base.EVENT_NAME, a.rm_code, a.rm, a.zone, base.SUB_PRODUCT_NAME, base.ACCOUNT_NUMBER, b.BUSINESS_UNIT_2_DESCRIPTION, base.CUSTOMER_SUB_CLASSIFICATION_CODE, a.Zonal_Head_ECN, a.Zonal_Head_Name, base.TRANSACTION_CURRENCY;

50000000 THEN 'A.<= 5 cr' ELSE 'B.> 5 cr' END AS GRANULARITY, COUNT(DAT.acct) AS acct , SUM(DAT.INT_ACC_MTD) AS INT_MTD , SUM(DAT.CR_ANR_LCY) AS CR_ANR_LCY , SUM(DAT.ANR_LCY) AS ANR_LCY , SUM(DAT.ENR_LCY) AS ENR_LCY FROM ( SELECT fbd.DATESKEY AS period_id , fbd.BRANCH_CODE AS SOL , da.ACCOUNT_ID AS acct , da.Customer_id , da.ACCOUNT_NAME , c.SHEDULE AS SCH , c.MAIN_HEAD_DESC , c.SUB_HEAD_1_DESC , c.SUB_HEAD_2_DESC , c.GPR_LEVL_DESC AS GL_DES , j.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION AS CUSTYP , n.code_description AS CUSTYPDESC , fbd.schm_type AS TYP , fbd.schm_code AS SCHM_CODE , da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE as acct_opn_date, fbd.c5code , fbd.npa_status , m.CODE_DESCRIPTION AS SCHM_DESC , fbd.CURRENCY_CODE AS CCY , fbd.CR_BAL_LCY AS ENR_LCY , fbd.DR_BAL_LCY , fbd.CR_AVG_BAL_LCY AS CR_ANR_LCY , fbd.AVG_BAL_LCY AS ANR_LCY , (fbd.NRML_ACCRUED_AMOUNT_CR_DLY_MTD * fbd.currency_rate) AS INT_ACC_MTD , fbd.currency_rate , fbd.SEGMENT_CODE AS seg , fdir.Interest_Rate AS ROI , fbd.Credit_Interest_Effective_Rate AS CR_ROI , fbd.Debit_Interest_Effective_Rate , fbd.CR_BAL_ORG , fbd.DR_BAL_ORG , fbd.START_DATE , fbd.MATURITY_DATE , fbd.contractual_maturity_days AS contr_mat , fbd.residual_maturity_days AS res_mat , (fbd.Sanct_lim * fbd.currency_rate) AS LIMIT_Amt , fbd.ENR_BAL_LCY , fbd.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE AS GL_CODE FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly fbd LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate fdir on fbd.ACID = fdir.ACID AND fdir.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND fdir.REPORT_DATE = (SELECT MAX(REPORT_DATE) from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate ) LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view da ON fbd.Account_No = da.Account_Number LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_glpl c ON fbd.GLPL_ID = c.GLPL_ID_New LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_date h ON fbd.Dateskey = h.Dateskey LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.customer.dim_customers_view j ON fbd.Customer_No = j.CUSTOMER_ID LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_branch k ON fbd.Branch_Code = k.Branch_Code and k.SOURCE_SYSTEM = ( select Branch_Source_System from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_branch_source_system where Branch_Source_System_Skey = 2 ) and k.etl_is_active = '1' LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code l ON fbd.NPA_Status = l.Code_Bkey AND l.Code_Type_ID = '92' LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code m ON fbd.Schm_code = m.Code_Bkey AND m.Code_Type_ID = '100' LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code n ON j.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION = n.Code_Bkey AND n.Code_Type_ID = '120' WHERE fbd.DATESKEY = ( select max(DATESKEY) as DATESKEY from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly) AND c.MAIN_HEAD_SR_NO = 3 AND FBD.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE BETWEEN '36000' AND '37999' AND FBD.AVG_BAL_LCY > 0 ) DAT GROUP BY DAT.period_ID, DAT.SCH , DAT.GL_CODE , DAT.GL_DES , DAT.TYP , DAT.SCHM_CODE, DAT.SCHM_DESC, DAT.CUSTYP, DAT.CUSTYPDESC, DAT.ROI , DAT.CR_ROI , DAT.seg , DAT.CCY , CASE WHEN DAT.ANR_LCY <= 50000000 THEN 'A.<= 5 cr' ELSE 'B.> 5 cr' END

SCRIPT: SELECT fbd.DATESKEY AS period_id , fbd.BRANCH_CODE AS SOL , da.ACCOUNT_NUMBER AS acct , da.CUSTOMER_ID as Customer_No, da.ACCOUNT_NAME as acct_name , c.SHEDULE AS SCH , c.MAIN_HEAD_DESC , c.SUB_HEAD_1_DESC , c.SUB_HEAD_2_DESC , c.GPR_LEVL_DESC AS GL_DES , j.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION AS CUSTYP , n.code_description AS CUSTYPDESC , fbd.schm_type AS TYP , fbd.schm_code AS SCHM_CODE , da.ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE as acct_opn_date, fbd.c5code , fbd.npa_status , m.CODE_DESCRIPTION AS SCHM_DESC , fbd.CURRENCY_CODE AS CCY , fbd.CR_BAL_LCY AS ENR_LCY , fbd.DR_BAL_LCY , fbd.CR_AVG_BAL_LCY AS CR_ANR_LCY , fbd.currency_rate , fbd.SEGMENT_CODE AS seg , fbd.Debit_Interest_Effective_Rate , fbd.CR_BAL_ORG , fbd.DR_BAL_ORG , fbd.START_DATE , fbd.MATURITY_DATE , fbd.contractual_maturity_days AS contr_mat , fbd.residual_maturity_days AS res_mat , fbd.Sanct_lim * fbd.currency_rate AS LIMIT_Amt , fdir.Interest_Rate AS ROI , fbd.Credit_Interest_Effective_Rate AS CR_ROI , fbd.NRML_ACCRUED_AMOUNT_CR_DLY_MTD * fbd.currency_rate AS INT_ACC_MTD, fbd.AVG_BAL_LCY AS ANR_LCY , fbd.ENR_BAL_LCY , CASE WHEN fbd.AVG_BAL_LCY <= 50000000 THEN 'A.<= 5 cr' ELSE 'B.> 5 cr' END AS GRANULARITY, fbd.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE AS GL_CODE FROM {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly fbd LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate fdir on fbd.ACID = fdir.ACID AND fdir.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND fdir.REPORT_DATE = (SELECT MAX(REPORT_DATE) from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.fact_daily_interest_rate ) LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view da ON fbd.Account_No = da.ACCOUNT_NUMBER LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_glpl c ON fbd.GLPL_ID = c.GLPL_ID_New LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_date h ON fbd.Dateskey = h.Dateskey LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.customer.dim_customers_view j ON fbd.Customer_No = j.CUSTOMER_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_branch k ON fbd.Branch_Code = k.BRANCH_CODE and k.SOURCE_SYSTEM = ( select Branch_Source_System from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_branch_source_system where Branch_Source_System_Skey = 2 ) and k.etl_is_active = '1' LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code l ON fbd.NPA_Status = l.Code_Bkey AND l.Code_Type_ID = '92' LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code m ON fbd.Schm_code = m.Code_Bkey AND m.Code_Type_ID = '100' LEFT OUTER JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_code n ON j.CUSTOMER_TYPE_DESCRIPTION = n.Code_Bkey AND n.Code_Type_ID = '120' WHERE fbd.DATESKEY = ( select max(DATESKEY) as DATESKEY from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.factbaldly) /* Placeholder for Power BI parameter */ AND c.MAIN_HEAD_SR_NO = 3 AND fbd.GL_SUB_HEAD_CODE BETWEEN '36000' AND '37999' AND fbd.AVG_BAL_LCY > 0 AND fbd.SEGMENT_CODE NOT IN ( 'BE' , 'AR' , 'BR' , 'SBR' , 'ST' , 'SST' , 'CCRT' , 'BL' , 'RA' , 'RET' , 'CAT1140123', 'RT' , 'LR' , 'CHC' , 'IG' , 'CFD' , 'IB' , 'ML' , 'GJA','PSGB','BCFD','DIY','FAR','PAR','PPC')

SCRIPT: select da.ACCOUNT_NUMBER, da.account_status, dc.card_number as CCARDNO, dc.issue_date as INSTDT, dc.FIRST_ACTIVATION_DATE as ACTVDT, dcs.CardStatusDesc as CARD_STATUS, dcc.CardCodeDesc as Card_Type from {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.liabilities.dim_accounts_view da LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.debit_card.dim_debit_card dc LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_bin b ON substring(cast(dc.CARD_NUMBER as string), 1, 6) = b.BIN_NUMBER and b.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.debit_card.dim_card_code dcc ON dc.PROD_CODE = dcc.CardCodeNo LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.debit_card.dim_card_status dcs on dc.CARD_STATUS = dcs.CardStatusNo LEFT JOIN {adb_datawarehouse_catalog}.masters.dim_card_product e on substring(cast(dc.CARD_NUMBER as string), 1, 8) = e.CARDPRODUCTNO and e.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 where dc.ETL_IS_ACTIVE = 1 and (da.c5code in ('AL', 'IE', 'SM', 'PS', 'BM') OR (da.ACCOUNT_TYPE_CODE in ('TWA', 'TVA') and da.c5code = 'SB'))
